data.description: Motivated Seller. Absolutely Stunning and 7 years young. Craftsman Style home with all the bells and whistles. Hardwood Floors throughout the entire home. Plantation Shutters/ Coffered Ceilings, Custom Built in Cabinets. Prepare to be Wowed when you step into the DREAM KITCHEN. Fabulous Island, abundance of cabinets , counter space and an oversized pantry. Plenty of space for everyone to gather at the island or Large Breakfast Area. The Main level also includes the Living room with fireplace/ Separate Dining/ Office/ Family room with Fireplace 1/2 bath and access to the Screened porch perfect for relaxing with your morning coffee. The Upper level includes Owners Master Suite with Spa Style Bath, tiled shower and water closet. You will never run out of room in the Master closet with a separate space that could be used for a small office or craft room. 2 bedrooms share a bath. The 3rd bedroom has it's own private bath. Best of all the upstairs incudes a Media Room. . Unfinished Basement stubbed for bath. Fenced in Back yard. Enjoy all those cool evenings by the stone Firepit. Must see in person to capture the beauty and quality of this home. Jefferson City School district. Showings begin 7/14...
